<div role="complementary" class="color-scheme-map column-large" data-view="map">

    {{#if user.email}}
        <div class="call-for-actions">
            <div class="call-for-actions-table">
                <div class="call-for-actions-row">
                    <a href="#resource-add-article" class="call-for-action" data-toggle="modal">Add<br/>Article</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="call-for-actions-table">
                <div class="call-for-actions-row">
                    <a href="#resource-add-action" class="call-for-action" data-toggle="modal">Add<br/>Project</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{#ifIn "admin" user.roles}}
                <div class="call-for-actions-table">
                    <div class="call-for-actions-row">
                        <a href="#resource-add-person" class="call-for-action" data-toggle="modal">Add<br/>Person</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{/ifIn}}
            <div class="call-for-actions-table">
                <div class="call-for-actions-row">
                    <a href="#resource-add-service" class="call-for-action" data-toggle="modal">Add<br/>Service</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="call-for-actions-table">
                <div class="call-for-actions-row">
                    <a href="#resource-add-organization" class="call-for-action" data-toggle="modal">Add<br/>Organisa&shy;tion</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="call-for-actions-table">
                <div class="call-for-actions-row">
                    <a href="#resource-add-event" class="call-for-action" data-toggle="modal">Add<br/>Event</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    {{else}}
        <div class="call-for-actions">
            <div class="call-for-actions-table">
                <div class="call-for-actions-row">
                    <a href="/contribute" class="call-for-action">Share<br>your<br>Story</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="call-for-actions-table">
                <div class="call-for-actions-row">
                    <a href="#user-register" class="call-for-action">Register for News&shy;letter</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <section id="user-register" class="map-view-hidden">
                <a href="#" data-action="close"><i class="fa fa-lg fa-times"></i></a>
                <a href="/user/" class="hijax transclude" target="_self">{{i18n "register"}}</a>
            </section>
        </div>
    {{/if}}

</div>

<div role="main" class="column column-small color-scheme-text bg-blue-palest">
    <div class="column-section clearfix">

        <h1>Welcome to the OER World Map</h1>

        {{#each scope.typeAggregation}}
            <table class="table table-statistics pull-right">
                <tbody>
                {{#buckets}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{doc_count}}</td>
                        <td>{{getIcon key}}
                            <a href="/resource/?filter.about.@type={{key}}">{{i18n key}}</a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                {{/buckets}}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        {{/each}}

        <p>
            Our goal is to provide the most complete and comprehensive picture of the global OER movement and to develop a global network of partners and volunteers to guarantee ongoing data curation. We currently gather data about people, organizations, services, projects and events related to OER.
        </p>

        <p>
            You can search our database <a href="/resource/">here</a>.
        </p>

        <p>
            If you have data you believe is relevant, please consider to <a href="/contribute">contribute</a>!
        </p>

    </div>

    <div class="column-section">
        <p>
            At the moment, we are focusing on gathering qualified data about OER Services. They can be browsed by <a href="{{getResourceUrl "https://w3id.org/isced/1997/scheme"}}">grade level</a> and <a href="{{getResourceUrl "https://w3id.org/class/esc/scheme"}}">subject</a>.
        </p>
        <a href="/aggregation/" class="hijax transclude map-view-hidden" target="_self">Aggregations</a>
    </div>

    <div class="column-section truncated">

        <h2>Recent Additions</h2>

        <a href="/resource/?size=9999&list=true&sort=dateCreated:desc" class="hijax transclude" target="_self">Resources</a>

    </div>
</div>

<footer>
</footer>
